{"tid":2402530,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食飯先定食餸先，其實已經反映到你係一個咩人。","createTime":"2021-02-10T12:59:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T23:40:01.000Z","uid":343520,"like":6,"dislike":115,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"9d1ea2bb3429eaca4999d05e854e2b0800579808","tid":2402530,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T12:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7RPgWJm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7RPgWJm.jpg&h=ec7da0e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鍾意食左餸先嘅人，即係鍾意先甜後苦，呢類人其實係好貪小便宜同唔挨得，唔想付出相應嘅努力就想得到回報，重視享受，貪圖逸樂，執輸行頭慘過敗家，重猜忌心，驚死食慢左人地會偷曬你啲餸。<br />\n<br />\n呢類人往往係面對唔到困難同挑戰，一遇到小小挫折，第一個諗法就係逃避同放棄。而且呢類人普遍係好愚蠢，比人講兩講就容易動搖，舉棋不定猶豫不決，絕對冇成大事者嘅氣量。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o8uAsTp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo8uAsTp.jpg&h=e7323eff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相反，鍾意食左飯（主食類，包括粥粉面飯etc.）先嘅人，即係樂於接受先苦後甜，佢地更加明白一分耕耘，一分收穫嘅道理，所以會更加刻苦耐勞，而且有容人之量同信任他人嘅心，佢地認為世上所有人都係善良嘅，唔會胡亂猜度他人。<br />\n<br />\n就算面對困難，佢地一樣可以迎難而上，勇於接受挑戰，因為佢地比其他人有更強大嘅內心同堅強嘅意志力，係值得大家學習嘅對象。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4nsyeAG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4nsyeAG.jpg&h=1815856f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於飯同餸一齊食，一次過塞曬入口嘅人，大概係對做人同自己冇乜要求，呢類人都不必多言，只需鄙視佢地。"},{"pid":"95619856020e5ca3c991ef68e0fb4aab0d7aeccd","tid":2402530,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:00:22.000Z","msg":"鄙視我吧"},{"pid":"34cea5cb7d91d0aa2efb6d2892ba3ac6462ea101","tid":2402530,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95619856020e5ca3c991ef68e0fb4aab0d7aeccd","tid":2402530,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:00:22.000Z","msg":"鄙視我吧"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:01:42.000Z","msg":"你自己知道問題所在就要改喇"},{"pid":"00429529562381eafe823e4ac0fc3b409036e7b3","tid":2402530,"uid":383632,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:02:02.000Z","msg":"如果食餸唔食飯咁點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16bae05a8a866840e996df9dff484692ad079830","tid":2402530,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:02:13.000Z","msg":"淨係食餸唔食飯🥺"},{"pid":"2d2328e6f527ca638472c223caec764b6f656e4e","tid":2402530,"uid":207390,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:02:26.000Z","msg":"出POST討論人地食飯定食餸嘅人，冇所事事<br />\n回覆嘅人，無聊至極"},{"pid":"b6ef03c41369af55540e2c6a3a871bb4371c5c0a","tid":2402530,"uid":159653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:03:02.000Z","msg":"我中意食菜先 一嚟就食肉會破壞咗味蕾 食其他嘢無咁好食"},{"pid":"10e7318748e7b36aed69b7d74c4535e1a4f9fc8c","tid":2402530,"uid":159653,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"2d2328e6f527ca638472c223caec764b6f656e4e","tid":2402530,"uid":207390,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:02:26.000Z","msg":"出POST討論人地食飯定食餸嘅人，冇所事事<br />\n回覆嘅人，無聊至極"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:03:21.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩，傻西"},{"pid":"02a1025f51efb651edb40a70a9d756a3a97c6c42","tid":2402530,"uid":343520,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"00429529562381eafe823e4ac0fc3b409036e7b3","tid":2402530,"uid":383632,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:02:02.000Z","msg":"如果食餸唔食飯咁點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:03:25.000Z","msg":"大致上Same as 第一類人（食餸先），不過更差，因為你做唔到有始有終，冇完成自己應有嘅責任。"},{"pid":"bf9e4b94031d200c6799e484261f7d59f9ab12d2","tid":2402530,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:04:00.000Z","msg":"唔食麵粉飯呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5305e989480fa6b0c32f6f6d8ea606055d5b96b2","tid":2402530,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2d2328e6f527ca638472c223caec764b6f656e4e","tid":2402530,"uid":207390,"like":35,"dislike"